quran[52]{c,v,t}:
  68,1,"Nuun. Mi woo…óndirii ku…óol e ko …ìe mbinndirta ko!"
  68,2,"Aan a wonaa, sabu neema Joommaa o, kaangaa…óo."
  68,3,"Ko pellet, hino woodani-ma njo…ìdi ndi ta∆¥ondirtaa."
  68,4,"E ko pellet, ha…óa e jikku maw…óo."
  68,5,"Aray nde nji'aa, …ìe nji'a kam…ìe kadi"
  68,6,"ko hombo e mon woni kaangaa…óo oon."
  68,7,"Pellet, ko Joommaa …ìuri anndude majju…óo on laawol makko ngol, ko Ka≈ãko kadi …ìuri anndude feew…ìe …ìe."
  68,8,"Wota a tefto yeddoo…ìe …ìen."
  68,9,"He…ìe nji…ói si a newantono (…ìe), …ìe newano-(maa)."
  68,10,"Wota a tefto kadi kala …óuu…óu…óo woondugol, koy…óo."
  68,11,"…óuu…óu…óo √±o'ougol, …óuu…óu…óo yaarugol ba…ódi."
  68,12,"…óuu…óu…óo ka…ógol mo∆¥∆¥ere, jaggitoowo, bakkodi'…óo."
  68,13,"yo'ora-…ìerndeejo e hoore …óum, ke…ìiraa…óo nii(.…ìiy jina)."
  68,14,"fii o wonii joom jawdi e …ìi…ó…ìe."
  68,15,"Si aayeeje amen …óeen janngaama e [tawnde] makko, o wi'a: ""Ko tinndi adinoo…ìe""."
  68,16,"Aray nde min maandina mo e hoore kinal."
  68,17,"Min njarribor …ìe wano Min njarribornoo jey…ìe ngesa mba : fewndo …ìeen ngoo…óndunoo pellet, …ìe co√±at ba subaka ko …ìe daw…ìe."
  68,18,"…ìe itti tinaani [wi'ide] :""Si Allah ja…ìii""."
  68,19,"Jayngol immori ka Joomi maa ari huu…ìiti ba tawi he…ìe …óaanii."
  68,20,"Ba wa'iti wa jemma …ìaleejo."
  68,21,"∆Åe noddindiri bimmbi oon :"
  68,22,"""Kori ndawee ta ngesa mon, si tawii ko on so√±oo…ìe""."
  68,23,"∆Åe pokkiti he…ìe …óuumbo."
  68,24,"Won'de ""miskiino woo naatataa e mabba hannde""."
  68,25,"∆Åe ndawidi e …óawugol [wa'asu…ìe …ìeen] ko …ìe e…ì…ìu…ìe."
  68,26,"Nde …ìe nji'unoo ba, …ìe mbi'i: ""Pellet, min majjii [laawol ngol]""."
  68,27,"wurin ko min …óawaa…ìe!""."
  68,28,"∆Åur…óo …ìe mo∆¥∆¥ude oon wi'i: ""mi wi'anaano on : haanii ko cubbunhino…óon?"""
  68,29,"∆Åe mb'i: ""Senaare woodanii Joomi amen ! Pellet, hari ko min too√±…ìe""."
  68,30,"Wo…ó…ìe e ma…ì…ìe feewtiti …ìeya, he…ìe pelindira."
  68,31,"∆Åe mbi'i: ""Ee bone amen ! Pellet, hari ko min bew…ìe."
  68,32,"Hino gasa ka Joomi amen wattitana min …ìuri baan …óon mo∆¥∆¥ude. Ko ka Joomi amen ko min reer…óube e [ya'afeede] ."
  68,33,"Ko noon tigi woni le…ìte …óeen; ko lette La'akara …óeen non …ìuri manude, sinno he…ìe nganndunoo !"
  68,34,"Pellet, hino woodani goo≈ã…óu…ìe …ìeen ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe, Aljannaaji ne'ema."
  68,35,"Kere Min mba…óay jebbilii…ìe …ìeen wano bon…ìe …ìeen?"
  68,36,"Ko he…ìi on, si …óon √±aawira noon?"
  68,37,"Kaa ho…óon mari deftere, nde janngoton e mum?"
  68,38,"Pellet, ko woodani on e mayre, ko ko cu…ìoto…óon."
  68,39,"Ka ko podooje woodani on e amen, koolnii…óe haa √ëande Darngal, won'de pellet, hino woodani on ko √±aawoton kon?"
  68,40,"La…ìndii …ìe ko hommbo e ma…ì…ìe fawtanii…ìe …óuum?"
  68,41,"Kaa ko kafidii…ìe woodani …ìe? yoo …ìe ngaddu kafidii…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, si tawii ko …ìe goo≈ãu…ìe !"
  68,42,"√ëande belenru √±oroytee, …ìe noddee e cujjugol kono …ìe mbaawataa."
  68,43,"Hara gite ma…ì…ìe …óeen no heli, koyeera no suddi …ìe. Ko tawde …ìe noddeteno e cujjugol fewndo ka …ìe mbaawunoo...!"
  68,44,"Accidam e kala jeddu…óo ndee yeewtere; aray nde Min suynira …ìe nokku ka …ìe nganndaa."
  68,45,"Mi…óo nee…ìnan …ìe. Pellet noon, pewje am …óen ko tii…ó…óe."
  68,46,"Kaa a la…ìndi …ìe njo…ìdi, hara ko yo…ìugol ndi teddani …ìe?"
  68,47,"Kaa …ìe nganndu fii wirnii…ói …óiin, hara hi…ìe mbinndira […óim hujjaaji ma…ì…ìe]?"
  68,48,"Mu√±√±or √±aawoore Joommaa nden, hara a wa'aali wa wonndii…óo linngii ngii fewndo o noddunoo [Joom makko] homo sunii."
  68,49,"Si tawno mo∆¥∆¥ere immorde e Joomi makko hewtitanooki mo, ko pellet, o bugeteno e wulaa hara ko o pelnii…óo."
  68,50,"Joomi makko su…ìii mo, o wa…ói mo e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìeen."
  68,51,"Hay yeddu…ìe …ìeen e…ì…ìiinoo yuwirgol ma gite ma…ì…ìe …óeen, nde …ìe nanunoo Ja≈ãtoore nden, hi…ìe mbi'a: ""on ko kaangaa…óo!""."
  68,52,"Ndee [Alqur‚Äôaanaare] wonaani, si wonaa waajo winndere nde!"
